MARCSubfieldLabel: Make and model of machine (NR), Programming language (NR), Operating system (NR),
Justification for Mapping: rdam:P30162 is used to "record requirements such as the make and model of equipment or hardware, the operating system, the amount of memory, programming language, other necessary software, any plug-ins or peripherals required to play, view, or run the manifestation, etc." - CP 2024-03-21
Transformation Notes: precede values with subfield labels, separate subfields with ;
Problems with Mapping: rdam:P30162 can only be recorded as an unstructured description, so the RWO URI needs to be stringified, and we will not mint concepts for terms in $a or $c with a source of term $2 - CP 2024-08-06
